* Test Structure
** Folder Layout
***_ /tests/unit/
***_ /tests/integration/
***_ /tests/e2e/
** Code Organization
***_ Functions in .py files
***_ Not inside notebooks
***_ Import into notebooks as needed
** Running Tests
***_ Dedicated test notebook
***_ requirements.txt for dependencies
***_ pytest.main() invocation
** Why .py Files?
***_ Better code reuse
***_ Easier to test
***_ Version control friendly
@endmindmap
